## Out of scope here

- Cross-encoder re-rank → M6 stretch only
- LLM-based query rewriting → M6 stretch only
- Generation / refusal logic → Agent 5 (`generation/`)
- Vector store internals → Agent 3 (`store/`)

If a routing change improves recall but breaks Agent 7's golden set, that's a regression — fix the implementation, don't lower the bar.
